text: Rocketcrash is the first material released by The Mushroom River Band. It was recorded and released in 500 copies under the band's own label, Tea Pot Records in 1999. ==Track listing== #"Twin Lyrics #1" #"Super Insomnia" #"B.M." #"Loser's Blues" Category:The Mushroom River Band albums Category:1999 EPs
